data.description: Price Reduction Alert!  Amazing opportunity! Dream Home for the Outdoor Enthusiast!  Tired of looking for places to store your boat, ATVs, jet skis, and other toys? Look no further! This gem, located in one of the most sought-after neighborhoods, boasts an expansive yard that's tailor-made for the active family or the outdoor hobbyist.  Imagine this: A home just minutes away from all your daily essentials - be it grocery stores, medical facilities, tantalizing restaurants, or even Legoland. Not only are conveniences at your fingertips, but also the freedom of NO HOA constraints. The possibilities are endless!  Step inside to find a spacious 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven with a 3rd bedroom that can be a second living room, office or a movie room!  Armoire coveys with the home.  Both bathrooms have been recently renovated, exuding modern charm. The generous kitchen with eat-in space is perfect for both intimate dinners and festive gatherings.  Your vehicles are taken care of with an oversized 2-car garage and 2 carports that can accommodate up to 8 cars! And that's not all. The property comes with a durable storage shed, perfect for stowing away your gear or setting up a workshop.  Safety and functionality come hand in hand with features like fully fenced-in yard, hurricane shutters, front yard and back yard irrigation system, and a top-notch security system.  This property can be your sanctuary where you can live out your passions, store your prized possessions, and create a lifetime of memories. Dive into this opportunity now!
